### compare: rice + derica -> 3 markets, exactly one isCheapest
GET {{base}}/markets/compare?itemId={{riceId}}&unitId={{dericaId}}

### compare: tomatoes + basket (seeded in all 3) -> comparisonPossible true
GET {{base}}/markets/compare?itemId={{tomatoId}}&unitId={{basketId}}

### compare: illegal pair (eggs + 50kg bag) -> 400
GET {{base}}/markets/compare?itemId={{eggsId}}&unitId={{bagId}}

### compare: missing unitId -> 400
GET {{base}}/markets/compare?itemId={{riceId}}

### should return an empty comparison (no seed for this pair)
GET {{base}}/markets/compare?itemId={{oilId}}&unitId={{kegId}}




# TRENDS

### trend: rice+derica+Mile3, should have several submissions
GET {{base}}/items/{{riceId}}/trend?unitId={{dericaId}}&marketId={{mile3Id}}

### trend: a triple with one submission -> INSUFFICIENT_DATA, points length 1
GET {{base}}/items/{{oilId}}/trend?unitId={{kegId}}&marketId={{mile3Id}}

### trend: illegal pair -> 400
GET {{base}}/items/{{eggsId}}/trend?unitId={{bagId}}&marketId={{mile3Id}}

### trend: missing marketId -> 400
GET {{base}}/items/{{riceId}}/trend?unitId={{dericaId}}